Text.string: Just more reason to waste you!
We're getting chopped up out here!
I'm not going out like them!
No pain, no gain! No heat, no meat!
There's more where that came from!
Haha, fresh meat for the stew!
Toe to toe! Me and you, grunt!
I like your jacket, Vault Thief!
Check out the gun show on this girl!
Wanna go a few rounds with me, witch?!
I've never eaten a Siren before!
Two for the chop of one!
Aw, you brought a side dish!
Quick! Before she calls the mech!
Gonna scrap your mech when you're dead!
Can't go toe-to-toe, eh? Also I'm gonna eat your toes!
This is what I've been waiting for!
Bout time we had some action!
This is why I joined up!
Hot plate of boom, comin' up!
Why does this take so damn long?
Argh, I got heretics to chop!
I'm feeling like a stir fry!
I like my Vault Thief rare and bloody!
Gonna eat what's left of ya!
I'm gonna put you down, bitch!
C'mere, heretic. Got some lead for ya!
My life sucks, and I'm takin' it out on YOU!
Tyreen's gonna drink soup out of your skull! A cold one! Like gazpacho!
I'm gonna sit down and think about my life choices!
You're just another notch on my gun!
You think YOU'RE big and bad? HA!
You want a piece of me? Cause I'm taking pieces of you!
I'm gonna bury you in a slow cooker!
I'll fry you up, Vault Thief!
I dunno what that is, but I hate it!
Smash it smash it smash it!
Turn it into a soup bowl!
Can't eat that. What's the point?
Don't make me come back there!
Holy crap, holy crap, holy crap!
Gah, I didn't sign up for this!
I am afraid and slightly aroused!
I'm not goin' near that thing!
She's so powerful! I just want to smell her!
One of you was bad enough!
Can I eat this guy too?!
[baby talk] Awww, duh wobot is scawed of us!
You're gonna be scrap when I find you!
Keep a lookout for the bot!
You're no good to me anyway!
I do not need this right now!
You can't kill us all! (beat) Probably!
Aww yeah! Eridium tier for me!
Ha ha ha! You got chopped!
I had a line for this...
What doesn't kill you makes you... [death rattle]
Serve me with... a nice red...
Joke's on you, I soiled myself!
Gonna stick this where the sun don't shine!
This land belongs to the C-O-V!
Hey, I ain't no classy lady!
Hey look, it's like a gun-dick!
Come on! Come on, Vault Thief!
I'm gonna be the one who kills you!
You WISH you could fight like me!
Come on, fam! Let's do this!
No one can stand against us!
This weapon is blessed by the Twin Gods!
Ready to chop this little pup!
I came for the Great Vault! I stayed for the murder!
By the power of the Twin Gods!
Be afraid, heretic! Be very afraid!
I'll make Eridium tier with your scalp!
Let's hurry this up, I'm hungry!
Gonna chew on you for a looong time!
You know you're healing me, right?
Stay right there and watch me kill you!
Please hold and wait for the kill!
Don't follow me unless you wanna DIE!
Mess with us and you DIE!
That was me. That was allll me!
Yes! I got 'em! I got the Vault Thief!
Need more of you out here!
Come out and fight with me!
Yeah! Now we got you outnumbered!
Say hello to my extended family!
